# shadcn/ui Components

This project uses [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/). Components are **not bundled** — each must be installed individually into `src/components/ui/`.

## Installing a Component

If a component is not yet installed, use:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add <component-name>
```

### Examples

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
npx shadcn@latest add card
npx shadcn@latest add input
npx shadcn@latest add dialog
npx shadcn@latest add badge
```

Multiple components at once:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button card input dialog
```

## Checking Installed Components

Installed components live in `src/components/ui/`. Check there before adding.

## Usage

```tsx
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"

<Button variant="outline">Click me</Button>
```
